Global Vagus Nerve Stimulation (VNS) Devices Market Insights
Vagus Nerve Stimulation (VNS) Devices Market size was valued at USD 1.65 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.78 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Vagus Nerve Stimulation (VNS) Devices Market Overview
The global market for Vagus Nerve Stimulation (VNS) devices was valued at approximately USD 2.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.8% from 2025 to 2030. The market growth is being driven by the increasing prevalence of neurological and psychiatric disorders, rising adoption of minimally invasive therapies, and technological advancements in VNS device functionality. As healthcare systems globally focus more on non-invasive therapies, VNS devices are poised to gain greater traction. Additionally, the growing awareness among patients and healthcare providers regarding the benefits of VNS in managing chronic conditions such as epilepsy and depression is further boosting market prospects.

